data.description: BEAUTIFUL 3-BEDROOM 3.5 BATH HOME! IMMEDIATE OCCUPANCY! OPEN FLOOR PLAN. SPACIOUS KITCHEN WITH ISLAND AND BREAKFAST NOOK OPEN TO FAMILY ROOM. ALL NEWER APPLIANCES, NATURAL FIREPLACE. BEAUTIFUL HARDWOOD FLOORING FLOWS THROUGHOUT THE FIRST FLOOR, LIVING ROOM, FORMAL DINING ROOM, FAMILY ROOM, BATH, AND KITCHEN. FIRST FLOOR LAUNDRY. SPRINKLER SYSTEM. A VERY PRIVATE BACKYARD WITH A HUGE DECK. NEIGHBORHOOD OFFERS BEAUTIFUL TREE LINED STREETS AND SIDEWALKS. MINUTES FROM AWARD WINNING MARSH BANK PARK, CLOSE TO M-5, LAKES, SHOPPING, AND RESTAURANTS. MOVE-IN READY.
